{
  "stem": "22869.6",
  "chunk_idx": 3,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 7.7,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "I don't know what you know what dried onions is.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "They used to sell them at that time.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "So we took a lot of this meat from the horse on the train, and we took the whole sack of the dried onions in our wagon.",
      "word_count": 27
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And I came back to the-- my old Jewish friends there because by now, I wasn't afraid anymore, you know, for my life as I was before, because I thought, well, if the guy's removed, maybe the cloud of-- of-- of the threat of the Jewish people is now diminished.",
      "word_count": 50
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And we boarded the plane-- the train, rather-- and we took off eventually from this place.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "And in the train we had a little more space, for some reason.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "I remember we could sit down.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "But we had no wood or no fire to heat up the meat.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "So we-- everybody was satisfied, satiated at that time from the food that the people, the civilians, brought, but thought for later on we have now an iron ration, so to call, save for the next day.",
      "word_count": 37
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So in the next days, what we were working-- everybody was peeling with their nails chips of wood from the side of the train.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "They were all from wood.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Everybody had a job to peel.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "I don't know if you ever watched a movie that-- that-- they-- they-- they-- where the guy was chipping with a little nail file every day a little bit piece of cement there, until he made a hole.",
      "word_count": 38
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "So eventually, we accumulated enough wood.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "Somebody had some matches.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "We lit some matches, and we took some of the meat.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "We used to heat it up, you know, with a match for two seconds.",
      "word_count": 14
    }
  ],
